hadiths[28]{hadithnumber,text}:
4470,ibne-Juraij ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar logon ko unke da'won ke mutabiq de diya jaey to bahut se log dusron ke khoon aur unke amwaal par dawa karne lagengey lekin qism muddua alaih par hai.
4471,Naafe-bin-Umar ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qism mudduaa alaih par honey ka faisla kiya.
4472,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik qism aur aik gawah se faisla farmaya, (yani aik gawah ki maujoodgi mein muddai ki qism ko doosrey gawah ka qaaim maqam banaya.)"
4473,"abu-Muawia ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Zenab binte-abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mere paas jhagdey lekar aatey ho, ho sakta hai tum mein se koi apni daleel ke har pahlu ko bayan karne ke lihaaz se doosrey ki nisbat zyada zaheen w fitteen (Sabit) ho aur main jis tarah us se sunun isi tarah iske haq mein faisla kar dun, to jisko main iske bhai ke haq mein se kuchh dun wo usey na ley, main is sura mein uske liye aag ka takra kaat kar de raha hunga."
4474,Wakee aur ibne-Numair donon ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4475,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Zenab binte-abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hujrey ke darwazey par jhagadney walon ka shor w ghogha suna, aap bahar nikal kar unki taraf gaey aur farmaya : main aik insan hun aur mere paas jhagda karne waley aatey hain, ho sakta hai unmein se koi doosrey se zyada zaban aawar ho, main samjhun ke wo sachcha hai aur main uske haq mein faisla kar dun. main jis shakhs ke haq mein kisi (doosrey) musalman ke haq ka faisla kar dun to wo aag ka aik tukda hai, wo chahey to usey utha ley ya chahey to chhod de."
4476,Saleh aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath Yunus ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki. Mamar ki hadis mein hai : unhon ( Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke darwazey par jhagadney walon ka shor suna.
4477,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Hind binte-Utba (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (bait ke liye) hazir huin to kaha : Allah ke rasool! Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) kanjoos aadmi hain, wo mujhey itna kharch nahi detey jo mujhey aur mere bachchon ko kafi ho jaey, siwaey iske jo main iske maal mein se uski la-ilmi mein ley lun, to kya usmein mujh par koi gunah hoga? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Maruf tareeqey se unke maal mein se (bas) itna le liya karo jo tumhen aur tumharey bachchon ko kafi ho."
4478,"Abdullah-bin-Numair, Wakee, Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad aur Suhak bin Usman sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki."
4479,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hind (Raziallahu anhu)) bait ke liye) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin to kaha : Allah ke rasool! Allah ki qism ! (pahley ( poori zamin par aap ke gharaaney se badh kar kisi gharaaney ke barey mein ye baat nahi chahti thi ke Allah unhein zaleel karey aur) ab eman laney ke baad) poori zamin par aap ke gharaaney se badh kar main kisi gharaaney ke barey mein ye nahi chahti ke Allah unhein izzat de. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! aur bhi (zyada tum ye chahogi.) phir unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) maal rok kar rakhney waley aadmi hain. to kya mujh par is baat mein koi harj hai ke main unki ijazat ke baghair unke maal mein se unke ghar walon par kharch karun? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par koi harj nahi ke tum Maruf tareeqey se un par kharch karo."
4480,"Zohri ke bhatijey ne hamein apne chacha se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Hind binte- Utba-bin- Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) aain aur kehney lagin : Allah ke rasool! Allah ki qasam! poori zamin par aap ke gharaaney se badh kar kisi gharaaney ke barey mein mujhey zyada mahboob nahi tha ke wo zaleel ho aur aaj poori zamin par aap ke gharaaney se badh kar koi gharaana mujhey mahboob nahi ke wo baa-izzat ho. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! aur bhi (is mohabbat mein izafa hoga.) phir unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) kanjoos aadmi hain to kya (is baat mein) mujh par koi harj hai ke main, jo kuchh uska hai, usmein se apne bachchon ( ghar walon ( ko khilaaun ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : nahi, magar dastoor ke mutabiq khilaao."
4481,"Jarir ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah tumharey liye teen cheezein pasand karta hai aur teen na-pasand karta hai, wo tumharey liye pasand karta hai ke tum uski ibadat karo aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik na karo aur sab mil kar Allah ki rassi ko mazbooti se thaam lo aur firqon mein na bato aur wo tumharey liye fuzool baton, kasarate-sawal aur maal zaaye karne ko na-pasand karta hai."
4482,"abu-Awana ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne ( na-pasand karta hai ki jagah ( naraz rehta hai kaha aur unhon-ne firqon mein na bato (ka jumla ( bayan nahi kya."
4483,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Warraad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : bila shubah izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne tum par maaon ki nafarmani, betiyon ko zinda dargor karne aur rokna, lao (doosrey ke huquq dabaaney aur jo apna nahi usey hasil karne) ko haram kya hai aur tumharey liye fuzool baaton, kasarate-sawal aur maal zaaye karne ko na-pasand kya hai."
4484,"Sheban ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum par haram ki hain aur unhon-ne ye nahi kaha : bila shubah Allah ne tum par haram ki hain."
4485,"Shabi se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke kaatib ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf likha : mujhey koi aisi cheez likh kar bhejein jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho. to unhon-ne unko likha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : bila shubah Allah ne tumharey liye teen chizon ko na-pasand kya hai : fuzool baatein, maal ka ziyaa aur kasarate-sawal."
4486,"Muhammad-bin-Ubaidullah Saqafi ne hamein Warraad se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Mughira (bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko likh bheja : aap par salamati ho. iske baad ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : bila shubah Allah ne teen cheezein haram ki hain aur teen chizon se mana farmaya hai is ne walid ki nafarmani, betiyon ko zinda dargor karne aur apne zimmey huquq ki adaaeygi na karne aur naajaaiz huquq ka mutalba karne ko haram kya hai. aur teen baton se mana kya hai : fuzool baton se, kasarate-sawal se, aur maal zaaye karne se."
4487,"mujhey Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad ne Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin Usama bin haad se khabar di, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula abu-Qais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : jab koi Hakim faisla karey aur ijtihaad (haqiqat ko samajhney ki bharpur koshish ( karey, phir wo haq bajaanib ho to uske liye 2 ajr hain aur jab wo faisla karey aur ijtihaad karey, phir wo (faisley mein) ghalati kar jaey to uske liye aik ajr hai."
4488,Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Muhammad-bin abi umr donon ne Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur hadis ke aakhir mein izafa kya : Yazeed ne kaha : maine ye hadis Abu-Bakar bin Muhammad-bin Amr bin Hazam ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki thi.
4489,"Lais-bin-Sad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin Usama bin haad Leis ne (apni) donon sanadon se yahi hadis Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad ki riwayat ki tarah bayan ki."
4490,"abu-Awana ne hamein abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi bakra se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne sajistaan ke qaazi Ubaidullah bin abi Bakra ko khat likhwaaya. padhi. aur maine likha. padhi. ke jab tum ghussey ki haalat mein ho to 2 aadmiyon ke beech faisla na karna kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : koi shakhs jab wo ghussey ki haalat mein ho 2 ( insanon / fareeqon (ke beech faisla na kare."
4491,"Hushaim, Hammaad-bin-Salma , Sufiyan , Muhammad-bin-Jafar , Shoba aur Zayda sab ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi bakra se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki jis tarah abu-Awana ki hadis hai."
4492,"Ibrahim bin Sad bin Ibrahim bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne hamarey is Deen mein koi aisi nai baat shuru ki jo usmein nahi to wo mardood hai."
4493,"Abdullah-bin Jafar Zohri ne hamein Sad bin Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qasim-bin-Muhammad se aisey aadmi ke barey mein puchha jiske teen ghar hain aur us ne unmein se har ghar ke aik tehai hissey ki wasiyat ki hai. unhon-ne jawab diya. iske tehai ko aik ghar ki sura mein jama kar diya jaeyga phir unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne aisa amal kya, hamara Deen jiske mutabiq nahi to wo mardood hai."
4494,Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumhen behtreen gawah ke barey mein na bataun? wahi jo shahadat talab kiye janey se pahley apni gawahi pesh kar de.
4495,"Warqa ne mujhey abu-Zinad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : 2 auratein thin, donon ke betey unke sath they ( itney mein) bhediya aaya aur unmein se aik ka beta ley gaya to usne (jo badi thi) apni sathi aurat se kaha : wo tumhara beta ley gaya hai aur dusri ne kaha : wo tumhara beta ley gaya hai. chunanche wo donon faisley ke liye Hazrat Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke paas aain to unhon-ne badi ke haq mein faisla de diya. iske baad wo donon nikal kar Hazrat Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ke samney aain aur unhein (apne mamley se) aagah kya to unhon-ne kaha : mere paas chhuri lao , main tum donon ke beech aadha aadhaa kar deta hun. is par chhoti ne kaha : nahi, Allah aap par raham karey ! wo usi ka beta hai. to unhon-ne chhoti aurat ke haq mein faisla kar diya. kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! maine us din se pahley (chhuri ke liye) sikkin ka lafz nahi suna tha. ham mudiya hi kaha kartey they."
4496,Musa-bin-Aqba aur Muhammad-bin Ajlan ne abu-Zinaad se isi sanad ke sath Warqa ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4497,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne chand hadisein bayan kin, unmein ye bhi thi, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aadmi ne doosrey aadmi se uski zamin kharidi to us aadmi ko , jisne zamin kharidi thi, apni zamin mein aik ghada mila jis mein sona tha. jisne zamin kharidi thi, us ne us ( bechney waale) se kaha : apna sona mujh se ley lo, maine tum se zamin kharidi thi, sona nahi kharid tha. is par zamin bechney waley ne kaha : maine to zamin aur is mein jo kuchh tha tumhen bech diya tha. kaha : wo donon jhagda lekar aik shakhs ke paas gaey, to jiske paas wo jhagdaa lekar gaey they usne kaha : kya tumhari aulad hai? unmein se aik ne kaha : mera aik ladka hai aur doosrey ne kaha : meri aik ladki hai. to usne kaha : (is soney ke zariey se) ladkey ka ladki se nikah kar do aur is mein se apne uper bhi kharch karo aur sadqa bhi karo."
